sources.title: The Rebel Set (1959) CRIME CAPER
sources.description:
Exclusive FRIDAY at PizzaFLIX Edition!
Directed by: Gene Fowler Jr.
Starring: Gregg Palmer, John Lupton, Don Sullivan, Ned Glass

Three disparate characters are summoned to a late-night meeting at a beatnik coffeehouse. Its owner has hatched a fantastic scheme that will change their lives forever. Co-stars Edward Platt, best remembered for GET SMART as “The Chief,” and features tragic beauty Vikki Dougan.
